@node bugs "Bugs"

 @{b}@{u}Bugs@{uu}@{ub}

The italian to greek translation may be not very 
precisely because I used a program (Ital2.99 of Arturo Ortino) 
to translate all the english words to Italian and a word
in english maybe have an other meaning in greek and other in
italian.

   I you find any contact me.. 
 
@endnode

